    "title": "Lead Investment Banker at Ujjivan Small Finance Bank",
    "description": "Grow your career with Ujjivan Small Finance Bank! We are hiring a Investment Banker for our Delhi team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Ujjivan Small Finance Bank:\nUjjivan Small Finance Bank is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ujjivan Small Finance Bank!",
